features.description: Commercial vehicles prohibited on US 441/Newfound Gap Road

core_details.description: Commercial vehicles are always prohibited on US 441/Newfound Gap Road and in all of Great Smoky Mountains National Park (with the exception of the Spur). Commercial vehicles will be stopped, turned around at checkpoints and may be subject to a federal misdemeanor violation notice and fine up to $5,000.
